# Trivy vulnerability ignore file
# Only add entries after security review confirms:
#   a) no fix is available upstream, OR
#   b) the CVE is not exploitable in this deployment context
#
# Format: CVE-ID  # reason — reviewed by — date
#
# Common base-image CVEs with no upstream fix yet:
# CVE-2023-4641   # glibc - no fix in debian bookworm — reviewed 2025-03 — low risk (no local users)
# CVE-2024-2236   # libgcrypt - no fix available — reviewed 2025-03 — not exposed externally
